channel.title: 377 Cache
channel.description: The client I'm working on for my server is having a bit of troubles. It has models that are overwriting the correct NPC models. I know the problems with the cache, but I can't seem to find a clean, reliable one anywhere. I've searched for.. going on the third day now. I'm hoping someone can point me in the direction of one, or give me any advice on fixing the problem.
